test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7b47e679d900>([90])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7b47e679d900> = [[1], [1, 90], [90, 1], [90, 1, 90], [1], [1, 90], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 30 == 90
 +  where 30 = <built-in function prod>([2, 3, 5])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
